    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">bugfix : a Taglist+minibufexplorer+ZoomWin interaction sometimes caused minibufexplorer to create a new window while ZoomWin was busy restoring the windows.&nbsp;&nbsp;ZoomWin then issued a complaint that it didn't know how to restore the new window.&nbsp;&nbsp;ZoomWin now temporarily disables events while it is restoring windows.<br></td>
</tr>
